---
// Full-bleed ambient layer, shared by every page: the warm bloom — slow-
// drifting radial gradients (slate-mapped), always visible. Generated at build
// time (no client JS) so it stays CSP-safe under script-src 'none'.
//
// The grain lives on body::before; the breathing grid is anchored to the
// masthead (Grid.astro), and the firefly motes to the title (Fireflies.astro).
// Neither belongs to this full-page layer.
---

<div class="atmosphere" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="bloom">
    <i class="b1"></i>
    <i class="b2"></i>
    <i class="b3"></i>
  </div>
</div>
